<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Blog Interaktif - Komentar Tersembunyi</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #fdfbfb, #ebedee);
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .article {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    #tombol-komentar {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      font-size: 16px;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    #tombol-komentar:hover {
      background-color: #2980b9;
    }

    #komentar {
      display: none;
      margin-top: 30px;
      animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    #komentar h3 {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #2d3436;
    }

    .comment {
      background-color: #f1f7ff;
      padding: 15px;
      border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(10px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>Blog Desain & Digital</h1>
    </header>

    <article class="article">
      <p>
        Selamat datang di blog kami! Di sini Anda bisa menemukan berbagai artikel
        seputar desain grafis, pengembangan web, dan strategi digital terkini
        untuk bisnis modern.
      </p>
    </article>

    <button id="tombol-komentar">üí¨ Tampilkan Komentar</button>

    <section id="komentar">
      <h3>üó®Ô∏è Komentar Pembaca:</h3>
      <div class="comment">
        <strong>bunga:</strong> Artikelnya informatif dan sangat mudah dipahami!
      </div>
      <div class="comment">
        <strong>khaleda:</strong> Saya suka tampilannya, ditunggu artikel berikutnya.
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <script>
    const tombolKomentar = document.getElementById('tombol-komentar');
    const komentar = document.getElementById('komentar');

    tombolKomentar.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const isHidden = komentar.style.display === 'none' || komentar.style.display === '';
      komentar.style.display = isHidden ? 'block' : 'none';
      tombolKomentar.textContent = isHidden ? 'üôà Sembunyikan Komentar' : 'üí¨ Tampilkan Komentar';
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
